<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><STRONG>Strength:</STRONG> 6<BR><STRONG>Stamina:</STRONG> 6<BR><STRONG>Agility:</STRONG> 5<BR><STRONG>Dexterity:</STRONG> 5<BR><STRONG>Charisma:</STRONG> 4<BR><STRONG>Intelligence:</STRONG> 6<BR><STRONG>Wisdom:</STRONG> 1</DIV>
