<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><STRONG>Attack:</STRONG> 5<BR><STRONG>Delay:</STRONG> 8<BR><STRONG>Damage:</STRONG> 8 (because bard weapons lately have been on the lower end of the spectrum, despite the lack of melee hits)<BR><STRONG>Range:</STRONG> 3</DIV>
<DIV><STRONG>Haste:</STRONG> 5 (because bard songs are plenty of haste, there isn't an absolute necessity)</DIV>
