<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ff0033>HP Regen:</FONT> Average, to useless.&nbsp; As a tank, regen does little during a combat<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Mana Regen:</FONT> N/A<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Endurance Regen:</FONT> Very Important, being locked to end, like knights are mana, we rely on this to function in all&nbsp;aspects of tanking in todays EQ&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ff0033>Strength:</FONT> Important<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Stamina:</FONT> ie hps, Very important<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Agility:</FONT> Important, surviability<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Dexterity:</FONT> Average, its nice to be more accurate.<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Charisma:</FONT> Low desire.<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Intelligence:</FONT> Low desire<BR><FONT color=#ff0033>Wisdom:</FONT> Low desire</DIV>
