				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				<DIV>So many responses already... I've skimmed over the posts so far, and they look good.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Once everyone has had a chance to post their opinions on the matter, I'll group all the posts up by class, and then try to consolidate them into a class profile that can be used as a reference when creating items.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
